		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">KGB</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">This article is about the <b>KGB</b> of the Soviet Union.  For the intelligence services in Belarus, see <a href="/wiki/State_Security_Agency_of_the_Republic_of_Belarus" title="State Security Agency of the Republic of Belarus">State Security Agency of the Republic of Belarus</a>. For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/KGB_(disambiguation)" title="KGB (disambiguation)">KGB (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<table class="infobox vcard" style="width: 20em; text-align: left; font-size: 90%; line-height:1.35" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3">
